* cascading styles
* tables
* lists (ordered, unordered)
* nested boxes don't accumulate margins
* border styles
* padding

Improved box model:
* Box has width/height/border/margin/padding
* Line < Box (?)
* layout_builder produces tree of boxes
* draw_box() calls box.draw, which calls draw_box on child boxes, etc.
* Line boxes know how to draw individual instructions
* draw_box takes care of setting x,y for each box, drawing borders, etc.
